title: Warhammer Fantasy Battles - ENG - Armybooks & Rulebooks - Latest
description:
Full set of the latest armybooks as of September 2nd, 2008. All are full quality high res PDF files, except for the Empire one. It is the only one on the internet, but its a bit on hte lower end of scans.

BONUS: I have also included Liber Chaotica Complete, Liber Necris, and The Life of Sigmar in this Torrent. They are great reads, especially Liber Chaotica.
